So we're just going
to fish and eat.

00:22:45.740 --> 00:22:48.234
- Here fishy,
fishy, fishy, fishy.

00:22:48.234 --> 00:22:48.900
Oh, there he is.

00:22:48.900 --> 00:22:50.024
Right there.

00:22:50.024 --> 00:22:52.886
