00:45:33.550 --> 00:45:37.180
all the garbage she produces in
a year in one small Mason jar.

00:45:37.180 --> 00:45:39.370
So it can be done.

00:45:39.370 --> 00:45:41.890
And the role of
influencers a new campaign

00:45:41.890 --> 00:45:44.830
from Adrian Grenier and
the Lonely Whale Foundation

00:45:44.830 --> 00:45:47.380
to try and combat
our straw obsession.

00:45:47.380 --> 00:45:51.320
And the campaign
is #stopsucking.

00:45:51.320 --> 00:45:54.820
So influencers can
play a great role here.

00:45:54.820 --> 00:45:59.410
And finally, what we do in
our home, on our campus,

00:45:59.410 --> 00:46:01.300
in our family, can really
have ripple effects

00:46:01.300 --> 00:46:02.952
that we might never anticipate.

00:46:02.952 --> 00:46:04.660
And that was the case
with these students

00:46:04.660 --> 00:46:07.600
from a middle school in Los
