00:46:14.374 --> 00:46:15.790
They got rid of
the tray, and they

00:46:15.790 --> 00:46:17.860
saved their school $12,000.

00:46:17.860 --> 00:46:19.535
This is a public
school in one year.

00:46:19.535 --> 00:46:21.160
That got the attention
of the district,

00:46:21.160 --> 00:46:24.550
and they banned Styrofoam trays
across the entire district.

00:46:24.550 --> 00:46:27.250
So again, these actions can
have far-reaching consequences

00:46:27.250 --> 00:46:29.410
that we might never imagine.

